        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "In fish, it looks like the ghost text shows the latest match, but pressing `<Up>` will take you to the one before that, whereas pressing `<Right>` will complete the ghost text.\n\nAlso in fish, as you move up through the history, it has your search highlighted. Once you press a key other than `<Up>`/`<Down>`, it removes the highlight and resolves to that history item. If you wanted to keep navigating with that as your new search text, you can. I think that visual feedback would also be useful, though perhaps that's a separate issue.",
